QuestData.Title: Setting Sun Garrison
QuestData.Description: The mogu will not be able to maintain this attack much longer. We should be able to handle it here, thanks to your kind aid.$B$BMight you be willing to find Anji at the Setting Sun Training Camp to the west? She's been tasked with preparing fresh-faced pandaren to aid the cause. You could show them a thing or two as well, I imagine.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Anji Autumnlight at the Setting Sun Training Camp.
